PuzzleGame.Spirit

类 Car

  • java.lang.Object
    • PuzzleGame.Spirit.Car

  • public class Car
extends java.lang.Object
    This class record the basic information of the car, and the method of generating the car path.
    Function:
    Draw the path at the end of placing the puzzle, include judging whether the path is draw successfully and the running of the car.

      • getCarImage

        public javafx.scene.image.ImageView getCarImage()

        返回:
        carImage

      • getOutpoint

        public int getOutpoint(int inPoint,
                       int type,
                       int angle)
        This method is used to get the value of the exit point placed after the puzzle is rotated.
        参数:
        inPoint - The entry point of the puzzle.
        type - The type of puzzle, there are three types of puzzle pieces: hyperbolic, cross straight and arc.
        angle - Angle of rotation of puzzle pieces before placement.
        返回:
        nowOutPoint

      • getInPoint

        public int getInPoint(int outPoint)
        This method calculates the entry point to return the next puzzle piece.
        参数:
        outPoint - The exit point value of the last puzzle piece.
        返回:
        The value of next entry point.

      • getNextPieceX

        public static int getNextPieceX(int X,
                                int outPoint)
        The method is to calculate the map x-coordinates for the next piece of the puzzle.
        参数:
        X - The x-coordinate of the previous map.
        outPoint - The exit point value of the last puzzle piece.
        返回:
        The x-coordinate of the next map.

      • getNextPieceY

        public static int getNextPieceY(int Y,
                                int outPoint)
        The method is to calculate the map y-coordinates for the next piece of the puzzle.
        参数:
        Y - The y-coordinate of the previous map.
        outPoint - The exit point value of the last puzzle piece.
        返回:
        The y-coordinate of the next map.

      • paintPath

        public void paintPath(int x,
                      int y,
                      int type,
                      int outPoint,
                      int inPoint)
        This method is to plot the internal path of each map.
        参数:
        x - The x coordinate of the current map position
        y - The y coordinate of the current map position
        type - Type of current puzzle.
        outPoint - The exit point value of the current puzzle after placement.
        inPoint - The enter point value of the current puzzle after placement.

      • pathSegment

        public void pathSegment()
        This method is the main function for drawing a path by calling the previous class method.
